setTriggerTimeout 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Defines the time between condition satisfaction and trigger activation 
 (randomly from min to max, with an average value mid). If the last 
 argument is true, the condition must be fullfilled all the time 
.  
Syntax:  
 trigger setTriggerTimeout [min, mid, max, interruptable] 
Parameters: 
trigger: Object 
[min, mid, max, interruptable]: Array 
min: Number 
mid: Number 
max: Number 
interruptable: Boolean 
Return Value: 
 Nothing